144
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,480
I was really nervous during the exam.

145
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,400
It was much tougher than what you face now.

146
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,640
Whenever I got tired of studying,

147
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,720
I would read this book.

148
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,440
Universal Gravitation

149
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,720
Yu Xingchen

150
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,760
Compared to the universe,

151
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,920
we are truly insignificant.

152
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,480
The Gaokao is important,

153
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,520
but it shouldn't be your only goal.

154
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,160
I mean, son,

155
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,320
even if you mess up the exam,

156
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,680
though I believe my son

157
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,040
definitely won't mess it up.

158
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,920
Even if, worst case scenario,

159
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,160
you fail the exam,

160
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,480
we will still love you.

161
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:41,040
Hui Ge, let me ask you something.

162
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,520
Be honest with me.

163
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,400
If I start studying seriously now,

164
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,400
