253
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,360
But I should seize

254
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,440
this rare opportunity.

255
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,920
To experience again what I've long forgotten.

256
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,280
Besides Su Ruo,

257
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,560
